# Force text diff for source/test files. Without this, a NUL byte sneaking
# into a TS source (e.g., a path-traversal test using a literal NUL) makes git
# auto-detect the file as binary and silently render the entire patch
# unreviewable in `gh pr diff` and PR web UIs.
*.ts text diff
*.js text diff
*.tsx text diff
*.jsx text diff
*.json text diff
*.md text diff
